OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FOpponents of major infrastructure
OL,7,Fprojects will have fewer chances to
OL,8,F"frustrate growth" through repeated
OL,9,Flegal challenges, the Prime Minister
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer said he would end a
OL,13,F"challenge culture" that saw major
OL,14,Fprojects such as nuclear power plants,
OL,15,Fwind farms and roads delayed by
OL,16,Funarguable bids for judicial review.
OL,18,FNumber 10 said the changes would
OL,19,Fprevent "cynical" or "hopeless" cases
OL,20,Fcausing delays and increasing the cost
OL,21,Fof infrastructure projects.
