OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FOpponents currently have three
OL,7,Fopportunities to secure permission for
OL,8,Fa judicial review against a major
OL,9,Finfrastructure project ` firstly by
OL,10,Fwriting to the High Court, then in an
OL,11,Foral hearing and finally by asking the
OL,12,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,14,FBut under plans announced by the Prime
OL,15,FMinister on Thursday, the written
OL,16,Fstage will be scrapped and any cases
OL,17,Fdeemed "totally without merit" will be
OL,18,Funable to ask the Court of Appeal to
OL,19,Freconsider.
