OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister said: "For too
OL,7,Flong, blockers have had the upper hand
OL,8,Fin legal challenges ` using our court
OL,9,Fprocesses to frustrate growth.
OL,11,F"We're putting an end to this
OL,12,Fchallenge culture by taking on the
OL,13,FNimbys and a broken system that has
OL,14,Fslowed down our progress as a nation.
OL,16,F"This is the Government's Plan for
OL,17,FChange in action ` taking the brakes
OL,18,Foff Britain by reforming the planning
OL,19,Fsystem so it is pro-growth and pro-
OL,20,Finfrastructure."
