OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FThursday's announcement follows Sir
OL,7,FKeir's pledge before the election to
OL,8,Fput the Government on the side of
OL,9,F"builders, not blockers", as Labour
OL,10,Fsees improving Britain's
OL,11,Finfrastructure as key to its mission
OL,12,Fof securing economic growth.
OL,14,FThe Government has already committed
OL,15,Fto making 150 major infrastructure
OL,16,Fproject decisions by the next
OL,17,Felection, and on Wednesday announced
OL,18,Fchanges to environmental protection
OL,19,Frules to speed up building work.
