OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FIt also follows a 2024 review by
OL,7,Fplanning lawyer Lord Charles Banner,
OL,8,Fwho recommended streamlining the
OL,9,Fjudicial review process so claimants
OL,10,Fhad "fewer bites of the cherry" when
OL,11,Fseeking permission to bring a case.
OL,13,FThe review found that around a third
OL,14,Fof applications for judicial review of
OL,15,Fmajor projects were refused permission
OL,16,Fto proceed entirely, although it was
OL,17,Fnot clear how many had been deemed
OL,18,F"totally without merit".
