OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FLord Banner said he was "pleased to
OL,7,Fsee the Government acting on the back
OL,8,Fof my review", adding that "reducing
OL,9,Fthe number of permission attempts to
OL,10,Fone for truly hopeless cases should
OL,11,Fweed out the worst offenders".
OL,13,FAccording to the Government, more than
OL,14,Fhalf of decisions on nationally
OL,15,Fsignificant infrastructure projects
OL,16,Fwere taken to court, causing an
OL,17,Faverage delay of 18 months and adding
OL,18,Fmillions to costs.
