OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FOfficials pointed to cases including
OL,7,Fthe approval of Sizewell C, in
OL,8,FSuffolk, where campaigners spent 16
OL,9,Fmonths seeking permission for a
OL,10,Fjudicial review despite their case
OL,11,Fbeing described as "unarguable" at
OL,12,Fevery stage.
OL,14,FHowever, only some of the grounds in
OL,15,Fthe Sizewell C case were deemed
OL,16,F"totally without merit", meaning the
OL,17,Fremaining grounds could still have
OL,18,Fbeen reconsidered by the Court of
OL,19,FAppeal.
