OL,3,CPM vows to curb 'Nimby' court battles
OL,4,Cover major projects
OL,6,FShadow communities secretary Kevin
OL,7,FHollinrake said: "While we welcome the
OL,8,FGovernment taking forward Conservative
OL,9,Finitiatives to streamline the planning
OL,10,Fsystem, Labour's blocking of our
OL,11,Fefforts to cut EU legacy red tape,
OL,12,Fsuch as nutrient neutrality, so they
OL,13,Fcan align more closely with the
OL,14,FEuropean Union will hold Britain back."
OL,16,FHe also accused ministers of having
OL,17,F"sat on their hands" on implementing
OL,18,Fmeasures to cut bureaucracy, adding
OL,19,Fthat reorganising local councils was
OL,20,F"hardly a recipe for accelerating
OL,21,Fdecision-making".
